ents, and the generation of detailed reports. The system architecture will be based on modern web technologies, ensuring scalability, security and usability. It is expected that the implementation of this system will significantly improve administrative efficiency, reduce operational errors, and provide a valuable tool for students, professors, and coordination, facilitating transparency and organization of the defense process.','gerenciamento, sistema web, cursos de computação','2025-05-08 20:00:00',NULL,'Online','remoto',TRUE),
